{"tid":195842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵高層加薪三成至9,090萬","createTime":"2017-04-11T01:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T08:18:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2070a2c76229d9fe6b6bbf7e4e0b31c5eef0f839","tid":195842,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:40:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19986871&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19986871%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170411&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=eec1459e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19986871%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170411&h=c4c9b824\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19986871&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170411</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵高層加薪三成至9,090萬<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n港鐵行政總裁梁國權<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵事故頻頻但港鐵高層去年仍坐享高薪，據港鐵昨公佈年報顯示，行政總裁梁國權2016年薪酬達1,480萬元，較2015年加薪5%或70萬元。整個港鐵董事局及執行總監會成員薪酬，亦按年大升三成至逾9,000萬元。<br />\n梁國權自2015年3月才「坐正」出任行政總裁，此前他為署理行政總裁，因此其2016年薪酬按年上升，部份應是計及升職因素。梁去年收取基本薪金及津貼等為880萬元、退休金供款140萬元，另有460萬元表現掛鈎薪酬，總薪酬1,480萬元。<br />\n<br />\n核心純利按年跌13.3%<br />\n<br />\n另外，原是車務總監的金澤培去年4月升任常務總監，升職兼加薪一成，2016年全年人工920萬元。而接替錢果豐出任港鐵主席的馬時亨，則維持收董事袍金120萬元。整個港鐵董事局及執行總監會成員薪酬按年大升30.4%至9,090萬元。<br />\n港鐵去年收入為451.89億元，按年升8.4%，但核心純利為94.46億元，按年跌13.3%，主要受累於香港物業發展利潤大跌；單計鐵路業務利潤，則按年增長約4%至89.16億元。<br />\n■記者方楚茵<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n「大部份人異常冷靜撳電話」<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;3小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n東涌綫故障　300人困車廂<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;3小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n延誤兩小時　最少罰300萬<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;3小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n【蘋果照相機】停一停　壞一壞<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;3小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n港鐵電纜故障影響十萬市民觀塘綫癱瘓　八客送院　千人摸黑行軌<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;3小時前"},{"pid":"26fb66fa8f8ac7dfa231584a19305b18f56f5d92","tid":195842,"uid":56432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:59:24.000Z","msg":"肥上瘦下，你吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e619fbff59247ede90bf60d575cc33cb9e4b528e","tid":195842,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:59:01.000Z","msg":"狗鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cfdaacee308827895f03b9fb6e646f5c3f9ca5","tid":195842,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:02:29.000Z","msg":"做得好咪加"},{"pid":"b80ac12e296f0d36e754bb2241e2863161c62098","tid":195842,"uid":15090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:18:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做得好咪加</blockquote><br />\n邊度撚做得好呀睇過"},{"pid":"03c94f915171fa4fb10145f1790d6df86d707b37","tid":195842,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f38a406921a196f19b9d45f85edf0940a1c970","tid":195842,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做得好咪加</blockquote><br />\n邊度撚做得好呀睇過</blockquote><br />\n對公司黎講做得好嘛<br />\n賺到盡"},{"pid":"59cdb6624318626c032cfce760c62923b160d2fc","tid":195842,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:30:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做得好咪加</blockquote><br />\n邊度撚做得好呀睇過</blockquote><br />\n出名五毛來"},{"pid":"1a84dcc5fbf34401196bfee33c78c16e5b652ca5","tid":195842,"uid":66091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:33:08.000Z","msg":"上面管理層出事食花生<br />\n解決左件事先出黎見記者上報<br />\n難為下面個啲前線係出面